title: Year of manifestation [custom mix included]
description:
This is a lecture by Wendy Kennedy from 2010.

She channels the 9th Pleiadian Collective (Mrs. P).

I've included two versions of the lecture.

The first version is the lecture as it was received.

The second version is a custom mix that I made originally for myself.

It's the lecture with a few different effects added. The reason I did this is that I wanted something directed squarely at my unconscious mind.

I accomplished this by creating the custom mix utilising a hypnosis technique, which is designed to confuse the unconscious mind.

Enjoy.
